content.original: Our intelligence has identified an infamous war criminal in the service of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. We do not care about the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces, but the criminal must be brought to justice. And by 'justice' we mean 'dead'.
content.prevOriginal: Our intelligence has identified an infamous war criminal in the service of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. We do not care about the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces, but the criminal must be brought to justice. And by 'justice' we mean 'dead'.
content.content: Наша разведка обнаружила печально известного военного преступника на службе у {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} на {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. Нас не волнуют силы {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, но этот преступник должен предстать перед судом. И под «судом» мы подразумеваем «смерть».

content.original: These are the coordinates that {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} intelligence provided, Commander.
content.prevOriginal: These are the coordinates that {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} intelligence provided, Commander.
content.content: Это координаты, которые предоставила разведка {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name}, командир.

content.original: The {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} target is believed to be here.
content.prevOriginal: The {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} target is believed to be here.
content.content: Предполагается, что цель {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} находится здесь.

content.original: Up to you if you want to clean up the other units; there's a bonus in it if we do. Good luck; Oliveira out.
content.prevOriginal: Up to you if you want to clean up the other units; there's a bonus in it if we do. Good luck; Oliveira out.
content.content: На ваше усмотрение, можете уничтожить оставшиеся силы противника; нам выплатят бонус, если сделаем это. Удачи. Оливейра, конец связи.

content.original: That's a wrap. Good work, everyone.
content.prevOriginal: That's a wrap. Good work, everyone.
content.content: Всё как по маслу. Хорошая работа.

content.original: That certainly could have gone better, Commander. I'm pulling us out.
content.prevOriginal: That certainly could have gone better, Commander. I'm pulling us out.
content.content: Могло быть и лучше, командир. Эвакуируемся.

content.original: The target is down. Head for the evac zone.
content.prevOriginal: The target is down. Head for the evac zone.
content.content: Цель уничтожена. Направляйтесь к зоне эвакуации.

content.original: Readings indicate the ambushing units are out of commission. The employer will be pleased.
content.prevOriginal: Readings indicate the ambushing units are out of commission. The employer will be pleased.
content.content: Судя по нашим данным, силы, устроившие засаду, выведены из строя. Работодатель будет доволен.

content.original: That is our target, sustain fire on that unit!
content.prevOriginal: That is our target, sustain fire on that unit!
content.content: Это наша цель, сконцентрируйтесь на ней!

content.original: Sensors are showing enemy movement beyond our initial count. Be advised you might meet with increased resistance.
content.prevOriginal: Sensors are showing enemy movement beyond our initial count. Be advised you might meet with increased resistance.
content.content: Сенсоры показывают движение противника, их намного больше, чем мы предполагали. Будьте осторожны, вы можете столкнуться с повышенным сопротивлением.

content.original: Commander, the target is bugging out! Eliminate them before they escape.
content.prevOriginal: Commander, the target is bugging out! Eliminate them before they escape.
content.content: Командир, цель пытается эвакуироваться! Уничтожьте ее, пока не поздно.

content.original: The target seems to be just a low-level officer in the overall {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} scheme of things - just a link in the chain. We just need to dive in, take out the target and get out.
content.prevOriginal: The target seems to be just a low-level officer in the overall {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} scheme of things - just a link in the chain. We just need to dive in, take out the target and get out.
content.content: Похоже, что целью является младший офицер, в иерархии {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} - он всего лишь небольшое звено в цепи. Нужно быстро уничтожить цель и уходить.
